      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASKERN VIOLET (6) scored (25.46) last time out at this track in a Grade 6 and will break from box 6 for the first time. Goes very well at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Can continue on her winning ways. HARA'S FRANKIE (8) tends to take a while to wind up, running on to place two back before spotting a start latest and finishing on strongly into third (25.81) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Solid record here winning three races. Leading player again. BELLA GEORGIA (1) has been in the money at her last two runs, most recently when third (25.69) in a Grade 5 over 457m at this track. Can turn it around this time. VELOCITY COMMIT (2) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to bounce back.",
